      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The level rig consists of two tanks:\n\u2022 Storage Tank (source tank)\n\u2022
    Calibration Tank (measurement tank)\n\nOperation Logic:\nAt 0% level setpoint:\no
    No water flows from the storage tank to the calibration tank.\n\nAt 25%, 50%,
    75%, and 100% setpoints:\no Water flows from the storage tank into the calibration
    tank.\no The inflow continues until the target level (%) is achieved in the calibration
    tank."
